#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an10.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an10.3:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 10 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 10 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Ānisaṃsavagga "
msgstr "1. Benefits "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an10.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Paṭhamaupanisasutta "
msgstr "3. Vital Conditions (1st) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an10.3:1.1"
msgid "“Dussīlassa, bhikkhave, sīlavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti avippaṭisāro; "
msgstr "“Mendicants, an unethical person, who lacks ethics, has destroyed a vital condition for having no regrets. "

msgctxt "an10.3:1.2"
msgid "avippaṭisāre asati avippaṭisāravipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti pāmojjaṃ; "
msgstr "When there are regrets, one who has regrets has destroyed a vital condition for joy. "

msgctxt "an10.3:1.3"
msgid "pāmojje asati pāmojjavipannassa hatūpanisā hoti pīti; "
msgstr "When there is no joy, one who lacks joy has destroyed a vital condition for rapture. "

msgctxt "an10.3:1.4"
msgid "pītiyā asati pītivipannassa hatūpanisā hoti passaddhi; "
msgstr "When there is no rapture, one who lacks rapture has destroyed a vital condition for tranquility. "

msgctxt "an10.3:1.5"
msgid "passaddhiyā asati passaddhivipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti sukhaṃ; "
msgstr "When there is no tranquility, one who lacks tranquility has destroyed a vital condition for bliss. "

msgctxt "an10.3:1.6"
msgid "sukhe asati sukhavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti sammāsamādhi; "
msgstr "When there is no bliss, one who lacks bliss has destroyed a vital condition for right immersion. "

msgctxt "an10.3:1.7"
msgid "sammāsamādhimhi asati sammāsamādhivipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ; "
msgstr "When there is no right immersion, one who lacks right immersion has destroyed a vital condition for true knowledge and vision. "

msgctxt "an10.3:1.8"
msgid "yathābhūtañāṇadassane asati yathābhūtañāṇadassanavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti nibbidāvirāgo; "
msgstr "When there is no true knowledge and vision, one who lacks true knowledge and vision has destroyed a vital condition for disillusionment and dispassion. "

msgctxt "an10.3:1.9"
msgid "nibbidāvirāge asati nibbidāvirāgavipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ. "
msgstr "When there is no disillusionment and dispassion, one who lacks disillusionment and dispassion has destroyed a vital condition for knowledge and vision of freedom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.3:1.10"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, rukkho sākhāpalāsavipanno. Tassa papaṭikāpi na pāripūriṃ gacchati, tacopi … pheggupi … sāropi na pāripūriṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "Suppose there was a tree that lacked branches and foliage. Its shoots, bark, softwood, and heartwood would not grow to fullness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.3:1.11"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, dussīlassa sīlavipannassa hatūpaniso hoti avippaṭisāro; "
msgstr "In the same way, an unethical person, who lacks ethics, has destroyed a vital condition for having no regrets. "

msgctxt "an10.3:1.12"
msgid "avippaṭisāre asati avippaṭisāravipannassa hatūpanisaṃ hoti … pe … "
msgstr "When there are regrets, one who has regrets has destroyed a vital condition for joy. … "

msgctxt "an10.3:1.13"
msgid "vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ. "
msgstr "One who lacks disillusionment and dispassion has destroyed a vital condition for knowledge and vision of freedom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli5.5, sc2
msgctxt "an10.3:2.1"
msgid "Sīlavato, bhikkhave, sīlasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti avippaṭisāro; "
msgstr "An ethical person, who has fulfilled ethics, has fulfilled a vital condition for not having regrets. "

msgctxt "an10.3:2.2"
msgid "avippaṭisāre sati avippaṭisārasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti pāmojjaṃ; "
msgstr "When there are no regrets, one who has no regrets has fulfilled a vital condition for joy. "

msgctxt "an10.3:2.3"
msgid "pāmojje sati pāmojjasampannassa upanisasampannā hoti pīti; "
msgstr "When there is joy, one who has fulfilled joy has fulfilled a vital condition for rapture. "

msgctxt "an10.3:2.4"
msgid "pītiyā sati pītisampannassa upanisasampannā hoti passaddhi; "
msgstr "When there is rapture, one who has fulfilled rapture has fulfilled a vital condition for tranquility. "

msgctxt "an10.3:2.5"
msgid "passaddhiyā sati passaddhisampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti sukhaṃ; "
msgstr "When there is tranquility, one who has fulfilled tranquility has fulfilled a vital condition for bliss. "

msgctxt "an10.3:2.6"
msgid "sukhe sati sukhasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti sammāsamādhi; "
msgstr "When there is bliss, one who has fulfilled bliss has fulfilled a vital condition for right immersion. "

msgctxt "an10.3:2.7"
msgid "sammāsamādhimhi sati sammāsamādhisampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti yathābhūtañāṇadassanaṃ; "
msgstr "When there is right immersion, one who has fulfilled right immersion has fulfilled a vital condition for true knowledge and vision. "

msgctxt "an10.3:2.8"
msgid "yathābhūtañāṇadassane sati yathābhūtañāṇadassanasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti nibbidāvirāgo; "
msgstr "When there is true knowledge and vision, one who has fulfilled true knowledge and vision has fulfilled a vital condition for disillusionment and dispassion. "

msgctxt "an10.3:2.9"
msgid "nibbidāvirāge sati nibbidāvirāgasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti vimuttiñāṇadassanaṃ. "
msgstr "When there is disillusionment and dispassion, one who has fulfilled disillusionment and dispassion has fulfilled a vital condition for knowledge and vision of freedom. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.3:2.10"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, rukkho sākhāpalāsasampanno. Tassa papaṭikāpi pāripūriṃ gacchati, tacopi … pheggupi … sāropi pāripūriṃ gacchati. "
msgstr "Suppose there was a tree that was complete with branches and foliage. Its shoots, bark, softwood, and heartwood would grow to fullness. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an10.3:2.11"
msgid "Evamevaṃ kho, bhikkhave, sīlavato sīlasampannassa upanisasampanno hoti avippaṭisāro; "
msgstr "In the same way, an ethical person, who has fulfilled ethics, has fulfilled a vital condition for not having regrets. "

msgctxt "an10.3:2.12"
msgid "avippaṭisāre sati avippaṭisārasampannassa upanisasampannaṃ hoti … pe … "
msgstr "When there are no regrets, one who has no regrets has fulfilled a vital condition for joy. … "

msgctxt "an10.3:2.13"
msgid "vimuttiñāṇadassanan”ti. "
msgstr "One who has fulfilled disillusionment and dispassion has fulfilled a vital condition for knowledge and vision of freedom.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an10.3:2.14"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ. "
msgstr ""

